URL;VALUE=URI:https://eisenhower.librarycalendar.com/event/2026-academy-awa
 rds-contest-17721
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251230T215707Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251230T215944Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you a movie fan? Think you can pick the Oscar winners? Chec
 k off your predictions from this year’s Oscar nominated films. Entries w
 ith the most correct answers will be eligible to win prizes. In the event 
 of a tie\, prizes will be awarded by means of a random drawing.  One entr
 y per person please. Entries will be accepted at the Answers Desk until 5:
 00 PM on Sunday\, March 15th. Prize winners will be notified when prizes a
 re available to pick up.Ask for an entry form at the Answers Desk.
CATEGORIES:Movie
