 n hits. This week\, My Fair Lady. In 1910s London\, snobbish phonetics pro
 fessor Henry Higgins agrees to a wager that he can make a crude flower gir
 l\, Eliza Doolittle\, presentable in high society. 1964. Rated G. 2h 50m.
CATEGORIES:Movie
