SUMMARY:Environmental Wellbeing for Children
URL;VALUE=URI:https://eisenhower.librarycalendar.com/event/environmental-we
 llbeing-children-15679
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251028T154059Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260125T225214Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us to connect nature with our inner emotional landscapes. 
 Children will participate in hands-on activities\, including a "Planting 
 Feelings" exercise\, to visualize and understanding emotions\, as well as
  taking part in a brief yoga session. Kids will experience how their bodi
 es and environments influence their feelings\, laying the groundwork for b
 etter self-awareness and emotional regulation. Get ready to bloom!
CATEGORIES:Arts & Crafts,Community,Social Services,Health & Wellness
