  of making the world a little bit better place to live in. This year\, res
 idents of Norridge and Harwood Heights are asked to do something kind for 
 your neighbors\, your community\, or yourself.Drop into the Library to par
 ticipate in some of our kindness related events like our annual Puzzle Swa
 p and Craft Swap! Don't forget to visit us online at eisenhowerlibrary.org
 /kindness26 to find out about some of the other kindness-themed events hap
 pening in the community.
