 ft-supply-swap-17807
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260106T220356Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T212939Z
DESCRIPTION:Have craft supplies you no longer need? Looking for some creati
 ve inspiration? Join us for a craft supply swap! Drop off unneeded but usa
 ble supplies and pick up some new-to-you materials.New or gently used craf
 t supply donations will be accepted on Friday\, April 24th from 10:00am-3:
 00pm. Those who donate on Friday will receive early entry to Saturday's ev
 ent. You do not have to make a donation to attend. All items are free!Craf
 ters with an early entry ticket can attend between 10:00-11:00am. Early en
 trants will be given a limited time to shop to accommodate all of those wh
 o donated. They can re-enter during the public hours. Doors open to the pu
 blic from 11:00am-1:00pmSuggested donations: fabric\, thread\, scrapbook p
 aper\, crafting books\, craft kits\, jewelry making supplies\, yarn\, croc
 het hooks\, knitting needles\, stamps\, etc.
