SUMMARY:Campfire Tales: Nine Goblins
URL;VALUE=URI:https://eisenhower.librarycalendar.com/event/campfire-tales-t
 bd-19591
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260304T233743Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T205421Z
DESCRIPTION:Escape the ordinary with monthly discussions of science fiction
 \, fantasy\, and horror novellas. This month's book is Nine Goblins by T. 
 Kingfisher. In this tale of low fantasy and high mischief\, follow a troop
  of nine goblins through a perilous journey where they will encounter an e
 vil wizard\, a forest full of elves\, trolls\, monsters\, and most terrify
 ing of all… a human being.
CATEGORIES:Discussion Group
DTSTART:20260624T233000Z
DTEND:20260625T003000Z
LOCATION:4613 N Oketo Ave\, Harwood Heights\, IL\, 60706\, US
ROOM:2nd Floor Conference Room
