 state-rep-brad-stephens-dmv-event-19604
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260305T161144Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260305T161144Z
DESCRIPTION:Representative Brad Stevens and the Illinois Secretary of State
 's office are presenting a Mobile DMV event at the Library.Services Offere
 d: Renewal/Correction of Driver’s License\, New/Renewal/Correction of St
 ate ID\, Vehicle Sticker Sales (License Plate)\, Organ/Tissue Donor Inform
 ation and Registration (at time of DL/ID Renewal)\, Motor Voter Registrati
 on with Driver’s License/ID Renewal\, Real ID Applications. Driver’s t
 ests will NOT be administered.Registration through Brad Stevens' office is
  required. To register\, call 773-444-0611 or visit https://repstephens.co
 m/mobile-dmv-event/Seniors ages 78+ must visit an official Driver Services
  Facility to renew licenses.Payments for services must be paid by check\, 
 credit/debit card\, or money order. NO CASH.
CONTACT:stephens@ilhousegop.org
DTSTART:20260902T143000Z
DTEND:20260902T200000Z
LOCATION:4613 N Oketo Ave\, Harwood Heights\, IL\, 60706\, US
ROOM:2nd Floor Meeting Room
GEO:41.9640192;-87.811601
